nctions, as well as the anomalous elasticity of the tubules. Finally we\npresent a scaling theory for the shape of the membrane and its specific heat\nnear the continuous transitions into and out of the tubule phase and perform\ndetailed renormalization group calculations for the crumpled-to-tubule\ntransition for phantom membranes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Aug 1997 17:03:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Oct 1997 20:56:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 11 Dec 1997 04:31:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-25"}
