re gauge degrees of\nfreedom. Replacing one infinity by a flat interior leads to analogous results,\nbut with the reduced phase space $R^2 \\cup R^2$. The utility of the results for\nquantization is discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Aug 1997 17:53:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 Feb 1998 16:52:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-25"}
